dc:description: Weathered dish, showing abrasions & iridescence, has seven pinched designs on its unevely sloped outer walls.  Each design consists of a raised oval, with a protruding circular nodule in the center.  The designs are irregularly pinched and overlap in two places.  The base is uneven & a deep pontil mark almost breaks through to interior.  Bubbles on base, chip on rim and on interior base, near center.  Free blown of transparent, almost colorless, glass with yellow tinge.
